Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.16,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:27.29,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:41.27,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…这样的…太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.65,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不来救我 亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:53.07,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我会做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.16,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瓦隆之女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.30,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.62,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 起这么早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:53.92,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…在床上…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.93,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.51,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,龙绮华晶 龙的那个分泌物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.02,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.27,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 太丢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.81,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,很丢人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.56,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.86,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我不会笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.40,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎样的你我都会完全接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.24,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:21.99,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.08,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.50,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.05,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你 尿床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.88,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.51,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是龙绮华晶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.52,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那才更丢人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.39,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:05.54,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,被北方杰法洛斯帝国和南方谢普隆王国两大列强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.33,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,夹在中间的罗雷亚蒙骑士国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.58,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,育龙之国如其所称
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.71,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,以阿尔克斯特拉达大陆中龙的栖息量最多为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.55,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 这个人口不足500万的小国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.55,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,有着一个特殊的学院 安萨里邦骑龙学院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:28.14,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是个将被称为育龙人breeder并且和龙结下契约的少年少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.60,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,引向星路的学院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.95,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,849)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\t(0,700,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HF77D21&)}露卡·沙里宁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.24,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.25,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候居然三人一起辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.50,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么忙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.71,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,而且三人都是因为结婚而辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.88,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.97,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,最后还说 店长也快点找个好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.55,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,维若妮卡王女不也是单身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.93,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会为了工作活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.31,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.48,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 面试是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.48,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,当然合格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,太谢谢了 厨房的工作我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:51.78,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,厨房啊 在后台工作有点浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.50,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.33,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,负责楼层的任务就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.21,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 艾可休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.92,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.39,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为了修复横亘在人类和龙族之间的鸿沟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.81,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要相当多的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.39,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,双子宫之月 合宿终于快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:19.85,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在今天的全校集会上 会宣布选拔成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.40,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,荣耀的罗雷亚蒙圣龙骑士团的大多数成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.73,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,都参加过合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.78,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,堪称为精英之路的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.66,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 反正跟我们没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:32.91,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.25,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高级班一年级 朱庇特·迪昂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:37.96,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.79,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高级班一年级 亚里斯·瓦根同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.42,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.92,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,以上学生请到台上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:48.63,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一位今日缺席的合宿成员是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.55,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,基础班三年级 露卡·沙里宁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.10,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,又翘课了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.72,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这副样子还能入选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.43,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不能信服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:59.56,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 有这么多反对的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:03.73,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她将近三个月没来上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.65,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊 是叫露卡什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.11,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不知道啊 她不是学生会的书记吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.03,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.99,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,一次都没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:19.62,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡·沙里宁 以史上最小的年龄被任命为龙骑士的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.71,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,刷新了蕾贝卡姐姐的纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.71,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,刷新了蕾贝卡小姐的纪录？那家伙真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.21,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.18,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是选拔合宿的参加者名单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.39,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,果然跟我们没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.01,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.85,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最后宣布「特别推荐名额」的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:40.81,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.40,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,特别推荐名额？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:48.03,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为了照顾本次落选的学生 我们新增了这个名额
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有请选拔委员 学生会长蕾贝卡宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.41,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:59.04,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,根据特别推荐制度 我选择了一位学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.67,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高级班一年级 亚修·布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.09,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.89,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么选择了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.56,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前 你得到了名叫艾可的特别帕尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:26.69,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还击败了尸灰龙 击退了断罪的阿布杜妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.90,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问 你是有才能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.70,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 按照以往的选拔标准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.37,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会落选
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:44.25,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了让你参加合宿 我提出新设置一个「特别推荐名额」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.33,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我 特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.05,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.59,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我想发挥你的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.72,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我能对你寄予厚望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.85,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.27,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然偷听 这可不值得褒奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.15,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.03,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.16,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是不是梅芙舍那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.96,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材？开玩笑吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.17,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.60,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.81,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了了 不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.31,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.91,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 烟的源头是香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.96,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你们了 请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:12.13,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.30,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,请注意别嗅得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.68,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾贝卡说的话总是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.39,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我会小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.47,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,惊动别人也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.98,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 这具棺材又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:31.36,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材？不是的 这是耶库布莱德式的卧床
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.19,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是能在葬礼上直接使用的上等货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.44,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,果然就是棺材嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.03,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡生性纤细 不许太过责备她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.58,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡？那她就是基础班的 被选拔合宿选中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.37,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你们刚加入学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.42,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,是第一次见到她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.34,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡·沙里宁 是俗称「森之妖精」的耶库布莱德人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.34,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,她的种族精通药草学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.85,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,制作的药剂在世界各地广受好评
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:07.73,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面 耶库布莱德人中龙骑士辈出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.31,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,也是战斗民族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.81,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 露卡的实力也不容小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:18.99,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,她刷新了我的纪录 以史上最小的年龄被任命为龙骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:21.74,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.28,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后 你的帕尔高文的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.87,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.71,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你心中有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.08,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.96,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 不是我忘记了驾驭的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.05,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,而是高文拒载我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.47,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高文拒载露卡已有三个月之久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:53.52,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,只要找不到拒绝的原因 我们也束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.27,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 也不能那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:03.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是露卡和高文之间的星精路这一事实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.99,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样长时间下去 高文会有性命之忧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.96,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.30,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我会做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.26,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,艾瓦隆之女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.39,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,通过星精路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.86,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,龙会从人身上得到生命能量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.90,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然断了三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.88,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入学院食堂两周
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.67,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底地调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.72,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经充分掌握了他的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.01,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.36,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.82,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会想起那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.17,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.22,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.77,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,要去选拔合宿帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.35,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不能停业关店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.77,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 能让我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.82,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.78,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,艾可 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.33,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…你怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.29,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,来得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.76,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你慢慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.51,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.65,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗 艾可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.98,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了个噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,噩梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.11,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,梦里的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和尸灰龙相像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.24,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,但是又有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.37,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,有9只眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.91,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,十分巨大 无法辨明真身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.54,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种不可摧毁的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.21,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我明明不认识它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.84,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,却有一种以前见过好多次的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.40,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我来打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.86,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:36.16,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候害怕得睡不着的时候 别人是这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.70,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.79,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样一起睡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.08,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不会再尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:48.88,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你真心认为我还会做那种事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.09,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我刚刚的话没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.68,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你少给我得瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.69,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么精神的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.15,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.78,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}为什么龙族…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.12,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,艾可又恢复了以前的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.71,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 又在酣酣大睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:28.17,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的横在龙族和人类的代沟看来已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:33.26,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 还需要很多的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.01,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要很多是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.72,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,真的那么需要晚上的对话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.60,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你幻想的那种事100%不会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:46.02,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上的艾可 会是什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.32,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,果然会说「不要」之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.44,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.16,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:42.58,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾贝卡小姐 如何才能使露卡和高文恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.66,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么突然问我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.54,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直无法召唤出帕尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.46,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,最后终于遇见了艾可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.92,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,正是经历了这些的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.42,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,才更明白现在露卡的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.26,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 无法坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.68,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮助露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.89,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是没有方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.35,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.02,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着相当大的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.90,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是让你骑上高文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:19.16,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你驾驭尸灰龙的时候 好像感受到了它的意识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.41,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 有些模糊的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.25,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,与之同理 我想让你尝试骑高文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.12,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我会尝试的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.50,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.84,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡 能再和高文对话一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.47,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对话这个词太生硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.14,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你和高文说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.31,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.35,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那嘟囔什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.10,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.19,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.19,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:59.11,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.95,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,别盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.46,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡 我有很重要的话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.46,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.30,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你的角好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.56,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.60,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.81,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那我能尝尝么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.07,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不要舔我的角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.86,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在对高贵的龙族做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.49,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我一脚踩…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.25,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…求你了…饶了我…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.29,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,住手了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:20:00.55,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我再睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.64,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.93,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾贝卡在第七龙舍等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.93,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你们打算对高文做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.69,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我们什么都不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.27,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了你和高文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.57,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我这就准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.83,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.66,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,换衣服 为了见高文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.92,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,露卡 你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.42,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等下让亚修骑乘高文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.01,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是询问它拒绝你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.47,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 你要再和高文说说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.64,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能解决的话那最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.69,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.05,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.60,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:37.98,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:45.95,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,头盔 肩甲 上臂甲 护肘 前臂甲 马刺！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:54.62,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 银丽骑士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.67,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,记住千万不要胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:57.46,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.54,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,艾可 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:04.67,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说感谢的话 不如记得给我买可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.93,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.57,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高文 为什么你要拒绝露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.61,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.04,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,高文
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.33,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,在上方 亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:47.26,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:09.94,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,————————ED—————————
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:21.35,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:22.14,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 露卡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:23.85,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌不穿内裤的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:25.19,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然问这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.36,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你好像讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:28.82,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那么说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.86,0:24:29.53,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.53,0:24:31.70,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不算讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.70,0:24:32.32,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:34.86,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 我到底该选哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.11,0:24:35.03,Dragner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HCD9109&\fad(500,0)\pos(1608,855)}次回\N月下的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:33.65,Dragner opjp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:38.11,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}世界のど真ん中で君と出会えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:43.24,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}呼吸も出来ないくらいになって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:47.58,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}小さくトクントクンと始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.75,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}君と僕のナニカ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:58.13,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}さあもう一回空を教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:03.22,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}鳥だけが知るはばたく羽根の重さ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:08.26,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}みんなは何も知らずに憧れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:15.65,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}君はちょっと切ない顔で笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:21.40,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}僕にはね何もないでも君の涙が減って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.95,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}本気の顔で笑うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.53,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}ヒーローだってどんなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.91,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}なりきってやるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:33.16,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}絶対絶対絶対絶対離さない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:38.29,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}死んでも君だけのナイトでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.67,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}でも本気で泣いて君は怒った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.76,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}冷たくなんてさせない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.60,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}と僕は涙を拭く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.22,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}聖剣なんてなくだっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.19,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}勇者じゃなくだって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:05:01.78,Dragner opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}君一人を守りきれるのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:38.11,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}在世界的正中间与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:43.24,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}连正常呼吸都无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:47.58,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}有什么在轻轻地扑通扑通地跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.75,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}在你和我之间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:58.13,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}来 再告诉你一次天空的含义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:03.22,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}只有振翅的鸟儿才知道翅膀的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:08.26,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}大家却无知的一味的憧憬着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:15.65,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}你用悲伤的表情微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:21.40,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}虽然我一无所有 但是你的眼泪却减少了
