Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.53,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}无论是英雄还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.91,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}我都会做给你看
