Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:38.29,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}就算死也要一直做你的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.67,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}但是真心哭泣的你怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.76,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}决不让你心寒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.60,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}和我擦干眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.22,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}没有圣剑也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.19,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}不是勇者也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:05:01.78,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}只要能守护住你一人的话
